svg.title: A simple, stylized depiction of a laptop with metallic shading.

Two metallic cards. The first is labeled next/font and has an uppercase A followed by a lowercase A in the top left corner. The second is labeled next/image and has a traditional image file icon in the corner.
The upper half of the React logo, an illustration of an atom, peaks out from the bottom of this element. It has a metallic shading effect.
